channel.title: Pvp planet: stingazz isle bounty hunter world release
channel.description:
I RELEASE TO YO CUZ SCHOOL IZ COMIN UP AND I DNT WANA FALL BEHIND AGAIN SO HERE YO GOEEEE
[QUOTE]Yo. Im making a world 2 for my PvP Planet server, and a World 3, which is the same server but not with the BH stuff. Basically, altogether, 1 BH world, 1 PvP world, 1 Skill/Main world. (BH&MAIN use same chars).
BASE: Final Devolution 2.7
Features:
- best combat? Iclarity Is a bit better but Meh.
[B][U]What i've added:[/U][/B]
- PvP Targets (Once you get a good amount of EP, Within 1 Level) - EP system - Interface (Need Proper) - Fixed up the walking - BH Levels (122-126 for example) - PROPER cant leave Edgeville, no process shit, walks back the number of steps you walked in. - Hinticons: A arrow above head of target. - Clan Chat (Not Buggy!) - Glitches Fixed
[B][U]Need To Add:[/U][/B]
- Drops (EASSSYYYY) - Points (EASSSYYYY) - Shops (EASSSSSYYY) - Autocasting for ancient magicks (LOOONG)
Suggest some things too :)
[B][U]MEDIA:[/U][/B] [IMG]http://i29.tinypic.com/2h4gaic.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/oqyq7d.jpg[/img] [B][U]EP is like that to get targ quicker for me :D[/U][/B] [IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/2s6q5gz.jpg[/img]
- Timer stops when they come back into the wilderness. - Gain some EP for the person who stayed in the wilderness
[B][U]NEW INTERFACE:[/U][/B]
[IMG]http://i31.tinypic.com/nq3h8l.jpg[/img]
[B][U]REMAKE OF INTERACE:[/U][/B]
[IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/fyhis0.jpg[/img][/QUOTE]
Yah, has more updates aswell so check it out.
DL HERE:
http://uppit.com/v/113EC6VL
CLIENT INTERFACE:
[CODE] http://uppit.com/v/GQTJQE8G [/CODE]
CONTAINS CLASS9 AND THE SPRITES.
HAVE FUNNN.
IM FLAME-PKZ ON MOPAR BTW.
